{"tid":1503493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"chinazi 會否被字典收錄","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T10:32:59.000Z","uid":54921,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"70d65b83425e2b3980b3789cc54e537b82a4cb34","tid":1503493,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>回顧「Hongkonger」及「HongKongese」被字典收錄<br />\nchinazi 會否再下一城?</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n英國牛津大學出版社的《牛津字典》(OxfordEnglishDictionary,OED)網上版3月加入900多個新詞，當中包括「Hongkonger」及「HongKongese」，均可解作名詞「香港人」，而後者亦可當作形容詞，意指「香港的」。牛津大學出版社每季公布一次新詞，而《牛津字典》網上版會於3月、6月、9月及12月更新字庫，兩個關於港人的新詞3月起上載字庫，並新增「HongKongChinese」條目。<br />\n<br />\n曾在英國留學、熟悉當地文化的作家陶傑表示，經《牛津字典》收錄的詞語，在世界上有一定普及性及地位，今次新增了「Hongkonger」及「HongKongese」，相信是因為出版社認同香港人是「特別的華人」，才會特意收錄。//"},{"pid":"ea777727cb134f4b56d3008eee01ea9234e5df92","tid":1503493,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"會係政治表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下牛劍邊個唔想要支那留學生囉"},{"pid":"001fad3a62b20cfbce2837056233b33c2c707e43","tid":1503493,"uid":124803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"已收錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbd3b299241dac342669b6abc436bb6f513ef5d","tid":1503493,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"要係twitter推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd3b2472a089d8a71c5f0fdb67a2fd2d24c2040","tid":1503493,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea777727cb134f4b56d3008eee01ea9234e5df92","tid":1503493,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"會係政治表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下牛劍邊個唔想要支那留學生囉"},